Mongrel Here

* Homepage[http://pieces-of-flare.rubyforge.org/mongrel_here/]
* {Rubyforge Project}[http://rubyforge.org/projects/pieces-of-flare/]
* email jeremy at hinegardner dot org

== DESCRIPTION:

mongrel_here is a small static file web server for use when you need a
quick web server in a directory.  

== FEATURES/PROBLEMS:

== SYNOPSIS:

== REQUIREMENTS:

=== For running: 
* For a gem install keybox depends upon HighLine[http://highline.rubyforge.org] >= 1.2.6.

=== For development:
* rake >= 0.7.1
* rcov >= 0.7.0.1
* rspec  >= 0.7.3

== INSTALL:

* gem install mongrel_here

